	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Wow, just played through Cave Story on Wii.
<br />
<br />One of the best modern games I've played, haven't been glued to the screen like that in a long time.
<br />
<br />Fairly hard, no long tedious cut scenes, great controls, fast action, good stuff.
<br />
<br />Are there any other games like this I'm missing out on?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
