<br />Except for all the cut scenes.
<br />
<br />I dont' know if the Wii version is different, but the PC version was loaded with story breaks that were not skippable or even fastforwardable.
<br />
<br />It really killed the replay value for me.
<br />
<br />
<br />A word to all game developers:  always make cutscenes skippable.  Always always always.  Non skippable cutscenes is a huge flaw in any game.

		

